name: ''Fighting the biggest cancer killer of children and adults under 40'' - Car Window Sticker
description:
A car window sticker designed by The Brain Tumour Charity. Each car window sticker has The Brain Tumour Charity logo, website address and motto printed on it. The motto for this sticker is, ''Fighting the biggest cancer killer of children and adults under 40''.

These stickers are easy to apply and just as easy to peel off

name: Danielle's Journey Wristband
description:
A grey silicone wristband which represents the Brain Cancer Awareness Ribbon with pink text, one of Danielle's favourite colours. Each wristband comes in one size fits all and has the following text printed on it, 'Danielle's Journey #StayStrongKeepPositiveAlways'.

Wristbands are packed by Danielle in a small sealed bag with a label of 'Thanks' tied with a piece of string.

All proceeds from the 'Danielle's Journey' wristbands will go directly into brain tumour research with The Brain Tumour Charity through The Danielle McGriskin Fund.

name: Limited Edition Grey Wristband
description:
A grey silicone wristband with red and blue text which are The Brain Tumour Charity colours. Each wristband comes in one size fits all and has the following text printed on it, 'The Brain Tumour Charirty Danielle McGriskin Fund'. Each wristband also has The Brain Tumour Charity logo of a brain printed on the band. 

Wristbands are packed by Danielle in a small sealed bag with a label of 'Thanks' tied with a piece of string. 

This is a limited edition wristband which means there are only 100 wristbands and once they are sold there will be no more until March 2014, which is brain tumour awareness month. The wristbands are grey, as this is the colour of the brain cancer awareness ribbon.
